title: 12/28/20 – HOUR 2 – Does Dwayne Haskins Even Care About Football? PLUS, Brian Costello!
itunes:title: 12/28/20 – HOUR 2 – Does Dwayne Haskins Even Care About Football? PLUS, Brian Costello!
description:
Doug Gottlieb and LaVar Arrington fill in for Dan Patrick and talk about the end of Dwayne Haskins’ run with the Washington Football Team. Can the Chiefs flip the switch in time to make another Super Bowl run? Plus, they speak with Brian Costello of the New York Post about the what the Jets plan to do in the upcoming NFL Draft now that Trevor Lawrence will not be an option.
